msgid ""
"<personname><firstname>Ben</firstname><surname>Burton</surname></personname> "
"<email>bab@debian.org</email>"
msgstr ""
"<व्यक्तिनाम><प्रथमनाम>बेन्</firstname><surname>बर्टन</surname></personname> "
"<email>bab@debian.org</email>"

#. Tag: date
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "2003-03-07"
msgstr "२००३-०३-०७ ई"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<मन्वोल्नुम्>१</मन्वोल्नुम्>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifies <filename>Makefile</filename>(s) to add debug info"
msgstr "त्रुटिनिवारणसूचना योजयितुं <filename>Makefile</filename>(s) परिवर्तयति"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>adddebug</command> <group><option>-k</option></group> "
"<group><option>-r</option></group> <group><option>-n</option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>adddebug इति</command><group><option value=-k> -क</option></"
"group><group><option value=-r> -र</option></group><group><option value=-n> -"
"न</option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>adddebug</command> modifies the <filename>Makefile</filename> in "
"the current directory (and optionally in its subdirectories) to add debug "
"info (<option>-g3</option>). It will also remove optimisations (<option>-"
"O[1-9]</option>)."
msgstr ""
"<command>adddebug इति</command> परिवर्तनं करोति<filename> मेकफाइल</filename> "
"वर्तमाननिर्देशिकायां (वैकल्पिकरूपेण च तस्य उपनिर्देशिकासु) debug info (<option value=-"
"g3> -छ3</option> ). अनुकूलनानि अपि दूरीकरिष्यति (<option value=-O[11-99]> -"
"ओ[१-९] ९.</option> )."

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr "एषा उपयोगिता &kde; सॉफ्टवेयर विकास किट।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "विकल्पाः"

#. Tag: option
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-k</option>"
msgstr "<option value=-k>-क</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep optimisations (do not remove <option>-O[1-9]?</option> flags which are "
"removed by default)."
msgstr ""
"अनुकूलनानि स्थापयन्तु (न निष्कासयन्तु<option value=-O[11-99]?> -ओ[1-9]?</option> "
"ध्वजाः ये पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण निष्कासिताः भवन्ति)।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-r</option>"
msgstr "<option value=-r>-र</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Recursively search through all subdirectories of the current directory and "
"operate on every <filename>Makefile</filename> that is found."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमाननिर्देशिकायाः सर्वासु उपनिर्देशिकासु पुनरावर्तनीयरूपेण अन्वेषणं कुर्वन्तु तथा च प्रत्येकं "
"<filename>Makefile</filename> यत् प्राप्यते तस्मिन् कार्यं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-n</option>"
msgstr "<option value=-n>-न</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"compile without NDEBUG and NO_DEBUG being defined (makes <function>kDebug</"
"function> calls work)"
msgstr ""
"NDEBUG तथा NO_DEBUG परिभाषितं विना संकलनं कुर्वन्तु (<function>kDebug</function> "
"आह्वानं कार्यं करोति)"
